            <title>[SPARK-44528] Spark Connect DataFrame does not allow to add custom instance attributes and check for it</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-44528</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;```&lt;br/&gt;
df = spark.range(10)&lt;br/&gt;
df._test = 10&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;assert(hasattr(df, &quot;_test&quot;))&lt;br/&gt;
assert(!hasattr(df, &quot;_test_no&quot;))&lt;br/&gt;
```&lt;/p&gt;

